A must-watch for every cinema lover, thinker, artist, and dreamer.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji.

snippet.title: FRUIT MIXER | Colorful Healthy Fruits Mixed Recipe | Summer Health Fruit Recipe Making in Village
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we made a colorful and healthy fruit mixer using fresh fruits. We included apples, oranges, watermelon, strawberries, kiwis, mangoes, papayas, jackfruit, and more, along with soaked almond gum, basil seeds, and pure honey for added taste and health benefits.

The video beautifully cuts and shows all the fruits, making it refreshing and satisfying to watch. This natural recipe is perfect for all seasons, especially summer, and is a great healthy fruit recipe for kids.

ja.title: フルーツミキサー | カラフルでヘルシーなフルーツミックスレシピ | 村で作る夏のヘルシーフルーツレシピ
ja.description:
今日は村で、新鮮なフルーツを使ってカラフルでヘルシーなフルーツミキサーを作りました。リンゴ、オレンジ、スイカ、イチゴ、キウイ、マンゴー、パパイヤ、ジャックフルーツなど、様々なフルーツに加え、風味と健康効果を高めるために、アーモンドガム、バジルシード、そして純粋なハチミツを加えました。

この動画では、様々なフルーツが美しくカットされ、その姿が映し出されているので、見ているだけで爽快で満足感があります。このナチュラルなレシピは、特に夏など、どの季節にもぴったりで、お子様にもぴったりのヘルシーなフルーツレシピです。

fr-FR.title: MÉLANGEUR DE FRUITS | Recette de mélange de fruits sains et colorés | Recette de fruits sains pou...
fr-FR.description:
Aujourd'hui, dans notre village, nous avons préparé un mixeur de fruits coloré et sain avec des fruits frais. Nous avons utilisé des pommes, des oranges, de la pastèque, des fraises, des kiwis, des mangues, des papayes, du jacquier et bien d'autres ingrédients, ainsi que de la gomme d'amande imbibée, des graines de basilic et du miel pur pour plus de goût et de bienfaits pour la santé.

La vidéo présente tous les fruits avec élégance, ce qui la rend rafraîchissante et agréable à regarder. Cette recette naturelle est parfaite en toutes saisons, surtout en été, et constitue une excellente recette de fruits saine pour les enfants.

pt-BR.title: MIXER DE FRUTAS | Receita de Frutas Coloridas e Saudáveis ​​| Receita de Frutas Saudáveis ​​para ...
pt-BR.description:
Hoje, em nossa aldeia, fizemos uma mistura de frutas colorida e saudável usando frutas frescas. Incluímos maçãs, laranjas, melancia, morangos, kiwis, mangas, mamões, jacas e muito mais, além de goma de amêndoa demolhada, sementes de manjericão e mel puro para adicionar sabor e benefícios à saúde.

O vídeo corta e mostra todas as frutas com perfeição, tornando-o refrescante e prazeroso de assistir. Esta receita natural é perfeita para todas as estações, especialmente o verão, e é uma ótima receita de frutas saudáveis ​​para crianças.

es-US.title: MEZCLADOR DE FRUTAS | Receta de frutas variadas, coloridas y saludables | Receta de frutas saluda...
es-US.description:
Hoy en nuestro pueblo, preparamos una colorida y saludable mezcla de frutas frescas. Incluimos manzanas, naranjas, sandía, fresas, kiwis, mangos, papayas, yaca y más, además de goma de almendras remojada, semillas de albahaca y miel pura para darle más sabor y beneficios para la salud.

El video muestra todas las frutas con una cuidada selección, lo que lo hace refrescante y satisfactorio. Esta receta natural es perfecta para todas las estaciones, especialmente el verano, y es una excelente receta de frutas saludables para niños.

de-DE.title: FRUCHTMIXER | Rezept für bunte, gesunde Früchte | Sommerliches, gesundes Obstrezept im Dorf zuber...
de-DE.description:
Heute haben wir in unserem Dorf einen farbenfrohen und gesunden Fruchtmixer mit frischen Früchten zubereitet. Wir haben Äpfel, Orangen, Wassermelonen, Erdbeeren, Kiwis, Mangos, Papayas, Jackfrüchte und mehr verwendet, zusammen mit eingeweichtem Mandelkernmehl, Basilikumsamen und reinem Honig für zusätzlichen Geschmack und gesunde Vorteile.

Das Video zeigt alle Früchte mit schönen Schnitten und ist erfrischend und unterhaltsam anzusehen. Dieses natürliche Rezept eignet sich perfekt für jede Jahreszeit, besonders für den Sommer, und ist ein tolles, gesundes Obstrezept für Kinder.

it.title: Mix di frutta | Ricetta per un mix di frutta sana e colorata | Ricetta per un mix di frutta sana ...
it.description:
Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo preparato un frullato di frutta colorato e sano usando frutta fresca. Abbiamo aggiunto mele, arance, anguria, fragole, kiwi, mango, papaya, jackfruit e altro ancora, insieme a gomma di mandorle in ammollo, semi di basilico e miele puro per un gusto ancora più intenso e benefici per la salute.

Il video mostra e taglia splendidamente tutti i frutti, rendendolo rinfrescante e appagante da guardare. Questa ricetta naturale è perfetta per tutte le stagioni, soprattutto d'estate, ed è un'ottima ricetta di frutta sana per i bambini.

id.title: FRUIT MIXER | Resep Campuran Buah Sehat Berwarna-warni | Resep Buah Sehat Musim Panas yang Dibuat...
id.description:
Hari ini di desa kami, kami membuat campuran buah yang berwarna-warni dan sehat menggunakan buah-buahan segar. Kami memasukkan apel, jeruk, semangka, stroberi, kiwi, mangga, pepaya, nangka, dan banyak lagi, bersama dengan getah almond yang direndam, biji kemangi, dan madu murni untuk menambah rasa dan manfaat kesehatan.

Video ini memotong dan menunjukkan semua buah dengan indah, sehingga menyegarkan dan memuaskan untuk ditonton. Resep alami ini cocok untuk semua musim, terutama musim panas, dan merupakan resep buah sehat yang bagus untuk anak-anak.

hi.title: फल मिक्सर | रंग-बिरंगे स्वस्थ फल मिश्रित रेसिपी | गांव में गर्मियों में स्वास्थ्यवर्धक फल रेसिपी ...
hi.description:
आज हमारे गांव में, हमने ताजे फलों का उपयोग करके एक रंगीन और स्वस्थ फल मिक्सर बनाया। हमने सेब, संतरे, तरबूज, स्ट्रॉबेरी, कीवी, आम, पपीता, कटहल, और बहुत कुछ शामिल किया, साथ ही स्वाद और स्वास्थ्य लाभ के लिए भिगोए हुए बादाम गोंद, तुलसी के बीज और शुद्ध शहद भी मिलाया।

वीडियो में सभी फलों को खूबसूरती से काटा और दिखाया गया है, जिससे इसे देखना ताज़ा और संतोषजनक लगता है। यह प्राकृतिक नुस्खा सभी मौसमों, खासकर गर्मियों के लिए एकदम सही है, और बच्चों के लिए एक बढ़िया स्वस्थ फल नुस्खा है।

Experience the timeless romance of Bollywood's golden couple — Dharmendra & Hema Malini — in the super romantic song Jaan Ki Kasam, now remastered in stunning 4K!

snippet.description:
#hellobrotherfullmovie #johnnylevercomedy #salmankhan

Vishal, a policeman shot by tycoon Khanna, is saved by a heart transplant. He finds himself working with the spirit of his donor, Hero, to investigate the businessman's drug racket and seek revenge.
Movie - Hello Brother 
StarCast - Salman Khan, Arbaaz Khan, Rani Mukerji, Johny Lever, Shakti Kapoor
Director - Sohail Khan
Producer - Sohail Khan

टाइकून खन्ना द्वारा गोली मारे गए पुलिसकर्मी विशाल को हृदय प्रत्यारोपण द्वारा बचाया जाता है। वह व्यवसायी के ड्रग रैकेट की जांच करने और बदला लेने के लिए अपने दाता, हीरो की भावना के साथ काम कर रहा है।
फ़िल्म- हेलो ब्रदर
स्टार कास्ट - सलमान खान, अरबाज खान, रानी मुखर्जी, जॉनी लीवर, शक्ति कपूर

ko.title: 당신이 우주에 무료로 갈 수 있도록 제가 500만 달러를 썼습니다
ko.description:
지금 바로 완전히 무료로 셀카를 찍고, Space Camp CrunchLabs에서 나와 함께 가장 지루하지 않은 여름을 보내요: https://crunchlabs.com/SpaceCamp  
당신만의 우주 셀카를 여기서 무료로 받아보세요: http://spaceselfie.com  
이 프로젝트를 지원해준 T-Mobile 친구들에게 큰 감사를 전합니다. 이들은 혁신적인 위성 커버리지를 향한 진전을 기념하고 있어요.  
당신의 셀카가 Google Pixel 위에 띄워져, 우주 공간에 전시됩니다. 더 많은 업데이트는 @teampixel을 팔로우하세요! https://www.instagram.com/teampixel/ #googlepartner  
이 놀라운 프로젝트에 함께해 준 모든 분들께 감사드립니다:  
SAT GUS 제작에 도움을 준 Tyvak International의 빌드 팀에게 감사를 보냅니다! https://tyvak.eu/  
콜로라도 광산대학교의 폭발물 연구실(Explosives Research Lab)에도 특별한 감사의 말을 전합니다 https://erl.mines.edu/

ml.title: ഞാൻ നിങ്ങളുടെ സൗജന്യ അന്താരാഷ്ട്ര യാത്രയ്ക്ക് വഴിയൊരുക്കാൻ $5,000,000 ചെലവിട്ടു
ml.description:
നിങ്ങളുടെ സൗജന്യ സെൽഫിയെ കിട്ടിക്കുക, പിന്നെയെൻറെ കൂടെ Space Camp CrunchLabs-ലേക്ക് വരൂ — ഇത് നിങ്ങൾ അനുഭവിക്കും ഏറ്റവും കുറവാക്കിയ ബോറായ വേനൽക്കാലമായിരിക്കും: https://crunchlabs.com/SpaceCamp  
നിങ്ങളുടെ സ്വന്തം സ്പേസ് സെൽഫി സൗജന്യമായി നേടൂ ഇവിടെ: http://spaceselfie.com  
ഈ പദ്ധതിയെ പിന്തുണച്ചതിനുള്ള വലിയ നന്ദി എന്റെ സുഹൃത്തുക്കളായ ടി-മൊബൈലിനോട് — ഉപഗ്രഹ കവറേജ് എന്ന ചരിത്രപരമായ ഇടയിലേക്കുള്ള അവരുടെ നേട്ടങ്ങൾ ആഘോഷിക്കാൻ!  
നിങ്ങളുടെ സെൽഫി. ഗൂഗിൾ പിക്സൽ ഡിസ്‌പ്ലെ ചെയ്യുന്നു. അങ്ങെ സ്പേസിൽ. കൂടുതൽ അപ്ഡേറ്റുകൾക്കായിフォロー ചെയ്യൂ: @teampixel https://www.instagram.com/teampixel/ #googlepartner  
ഈ അത്ഭുതകരമായ നിർമ്മാണത്തിൽ സഹായിച്ച എല്ലാവർക്കും നന്ദി:  
SAT GUS നെ യാഥാർത്ഥ്യമാക്കിയതിന് സഹായിച്ച Tyvak International ലെ ഞങ്ങളുടെ ബിൽഡ് സംഘത്തിന് പ്രത്യേക നന്ദി: https://tyvak.eu/  
Colorado School of Mines-ലെ Explosives Research Lab-ന് പ്രത്യേകം നന്ദി: https://erl.mines.edu/  
ഈ വീഡിയോയിലേതിൽ ചില സംഗീതങ്ങൾ നൽകി സഹായിച്ച ഈ കലാകാരന്മാർക്ക് നന്ദി:  
Ponder - @Pondermusic  
Laura Shigihara - @supershigi  
Andrew Applepie - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie

pa.title: ਮੈਂ 5,000,000 ਡਾਲਰ ਖਰਚ ਕੀਤੇ ਤਾਂ ਜੋ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਫ੍ਰੀ ਵਿੱਚ ਸਪੇਸ ਵਿੱਚ ਜਾ ਸਕੋ।
pa.description:
ਆਪਣੀ ਬਿਲਕੁਲ ਫ੍ਰੀ ਸੈਲਫੀ ਲਓ ਅਤੇ ਫਿਰ ਆਪਣੀ ਸਭ ਤੋਂ ਘੱਟ ਬੋਰਿੰਗ ਗਰਮੀਆਂ ਲਈ ਸਪੇਸ ਕੈਂਪ ਕ੍ਰੰਚਲੈਬਸ 'ਤੇ ਮੇਰੇ ਨਾਲ ਸ਼ਾਮਲ ਹੋਵੋ: https://crunchlabs.com/SpaceCamp
ਆਪਣੀ ਖੁਦ ਦੀ ਸਪੇਸ ਸੈਲਫੀ ਫ੍ਰੀ ਵਿੱਚ ਇੱਥੇ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ: http://spaceselfie.com
ਟੀ-ਮੋਬਾਈਲ 'ਤੇ ਮੇਰੇ ਦੋਸਤਾਂ ਦਾ ਬਹੁਤ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ, ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੀ ਸਫਲਤਾਪੂਰਵਕ ਸੈਟੇਲਾਈਟ ਕਵਰੇਜ ਵੱਲ ਤਰੱਕੀ ਦੇ ਜਸ਼ਨ ਵਿੱਚ ਇਸ ਪ੍ਰੋਜੈਕਟ ਦਾ ਸਮਰਥਨ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ।
ਤੁਹਾਡੀ ਸੈਲਫੀ। ਗੂਗਲ ਪਿਕਸਲ 'ਤੇ ਪ੍ਰਦਰਸ਼ਿਤ। ਸਪੇਸ ਵਿੱਚ। ਹੋਰ ਅੱਪਡੇਟਾਂ ਲਈ @teampixel ਨੂੰ ਫਾਲੋ ਕਰੋ! https://www.instagram.com/teampixel/ #googlepartner
ਇਸ ਸ਼ਾਨਦਾਰ ਬਿਲਡ ਵਿੱਚ ਮਦਦ ਕਰਨ ਵਾਲੇ ਹਰ ਵਿਅਕਤੀ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ:
ਟਾਇਵਾਕ ਇੰਟਰਨੈਸ਼ਨਲ 'ਤੇ ਸਾਡੀ ਬਿਲਡ ਟੀਮ ਦਾ SATGUS ਨੂੰ ਜੀਵਨ ਵਿੱਚ ਲਿਆਉਣ ਵਿੱਚ ਸਾਡੀ ਮਦਦ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ! https://tyvak.eu/
ਕੋਲੋਰਾਡੋ ਸਕੂਲ ਆਫ਼ ਮਾਈਨਜ਼ ਵਿਖੇ ਐਕਸਪਲੋਸਿਵਜ਼ ਰਿਸਰਚ ਲੈਬ ਦਾ ਵਿਸ਼ੇਸ਼ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ https://erl.mines.edu/
ਵੀਡੀਓ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੁਝ ਮਿਊਜ਼ਿਕ ਦੇਣ ਲਈ ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ:

Laura Shigihara -  @supershigi

তাহলে একেবারে ফ্রি নিজের সেলফি তুলে ফেলো আর তারপর আমার সঙ্গে Space Camp CrunchLabs-এ যোগ দাও তোমার জীবনের সবচেয়ে কম বিরক্তিকর গ্রীষ্মের জন্য: https://crunchlabs.com/SpaceCamp  
ফ্রি-তে নিজের স্পেস সেলফি পেতে ভিজিট করো: http://spaceselfie.com  
এই প্রকল্পে সহায়তা করার জন্য T-Mobile-এ আমার বন্ধুদের প্রতি বড় একটা ধন্যবাদ, যাদের উপগ্রহ সংযোগ উন্নয়নের অগ্রযাত্রা উদযাপন করা হচ্ছে।  
তোমার সেলফি। গুগল পিক্সেলের স্ক্রিনে। মহাকাশে। আরও আপডেটের জন্য ফলো করো: @teampixel https://www.instagram.com/teampixel/ #googlepartner  
এই অসাধারণ নির্মাণে সহায়তা করা সবার প্রতি ধন্যবাদ:  
আমাদের Build টিম Tyvak International-এ, যারা SAT GUS বাস্তবায়নে সাহায্য করেছে! https://tyvak.eu/  
বিশেষ ধন্যবাদ Colorado School of Mines-এর Explosives Research Lab-কে: https://erl.mines.edu/  
ভিডিওটির কিছু সংগীতের জন্য ধন্যবাদ এই শিল্পীদের:

Chori bhul te na gayi re purane yaar ne
Ek tarfa thi thai andhi mere pyar ne
Gediyan pe gedi maari saans na liya
Chora aya tha milan kade laal car mein
Ankhya mein leke ghane khaab aya su
Teri khatir main chori re gulab laya su
Aaj bhi yo chaale se pasand teri gel
Mere fool ke liye main poora baag laya su
Billa sonipat aala fir zid pe adeya
Leke lamborghini tere gate pe khada
Mere pache dekh madama ki line laagri
Chora dheeth hai sire ka tere pache padeya

Teri na ho jisme vo kaam na karu

Teri aai hove aur pehla mein maru

Geet sonipat aale ke tu gaati chaliye
Visa lagwa ke baat diye sare gaam mein
Team all good aale dhool thate aaliye
Bhola baba dekh chore ki support mein khadeya
Jabe teri gelya ban teri jott mein khadeya
Meri kare rakhwali parchai vo meri

snippet.title: அமெரிக்காவை விட்டு ரொம்ப தூரம் போக போறோம் | புதிய பயணம் ஆரம்பம் | Episode 1
snippet.description:
Episode 1: “Wilderness Calls, the Glow Unfolds”

The journey begins… but where are we headed?

From the skies of Texas to a place where the air feels ancient and the trees whisper stories, I’m taking you on a cinematic ride through wild landscapes, tropical roads, and a destination I won’t reveal—just yet.

This episode is packed with clues. Watch closely as I cross oceans, follow green trails, and step into a world far from the everyday. The rainforest calls, and something magical awaits in the chapters ahead…

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4406: Taarak Invests Money
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak advises his boss to invest, making an investment himself as well. Later, Jethalal turns to Taarak for guidance on the same opportunity. But is it all too good to be true or just a scam in disguise?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4406 | 24 May 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1090480162

snippet.description:
अपनी बहन किरण की शादी के दिन हत्या के बाद किशन अपना दिमाग खो देता है। हालांकि, जब किरण की हमशक्ल काजल मदद के लिए उसके पास आती है, तो वह उसे उसके प्रेमी से मिलाने का वादा करता है।

Kishan loses his sanity after his sister, Kiran, is murdered on her wedding day. However, when Kajal, a lookalike of Kiran, comes to him for help, he pledges to unite her with her lover.

Movie Name - Himmatwala (1998) 
Star Cast - Mithun Chakraborty, Ayesha Jhulka, Shakti Kapoor, Keerti Chawla, Rajeev Verma, Tinnu Anand, Raadhika Sarathkumar, Tiku Talsania

snippet.title: Naam Jap Ka Asli Maksad Kya Hai? By Sandeep Maheshwari
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

snippet.description:

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: কৃষ্ণনগরে বন্যা | Gopal Bhar | Episode - 1154
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

The people of Krishnanagar are worried as continuous rainfall leads to flooding in the kingdom. Will Gopal come up with a solution in time?

Show Name: Gopal Bhar - গোপালভাঁড়
Directed By: Sourav Mondal, Hansa Mondal
Written By: Hansa Mondal
Original language: Bengali
Episode No: 1154

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #গোপালভর 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.
